{"tid":946931,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"紐亞寸紅軍後防好多缺點","createTime":"2018-12-19T01:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T02:47:56.000Z","uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"281b9da047305e157a1e834d4c1e1a1d58162a6a","tid":946931,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T01:34:25.000Z","msg":"歐聯16強完成抽籤，上屆亞軍利物浦將大戰拜仁慕尼黑，西甲班霸巴塞隆拿就抽中里昂。巴塞教頭華爾維迪滿意抽籤結果，仲開名話好開心可以避開勁敵利物浦。拜仁門將紐亞需面對埃及文明鋒線，就話紅軍後防有明顯缺點，拜仁一眾出色攻擊手必有理想發揮。"},{"pid":"990327731cce5286b96865fc8de772ce29df7072","tid":946931,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T01:34:29.000Z","msg":"「今季利物浦發揮唔錯，上屆歐聯亦殺入決賽。不過抽正拜仁，紅軍唔會覺得係好籤。佢哋擅於踢反擊足球，埋門觸角亦好犀利，但拜仁已經洞察到佢哋後防有明顯弱點，而且要應付拜仁一眾出色射手。」"},{"pid":"976ca07dec11ddde4b2c32425fb39ebe4125acc5","tid":946931,"uid":25758,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T01:35:35.000Z","msg":"扭呀：我失幾多粒，前面幫我入番幾多粒！"},{"pid":"5ca60a1387b9592fd90b01bef0921173471caecb","tid":946931,"uid":20756,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T01:36:01.000Z","msg":"Neuer本身自己就係弱點"},{"pid":"745e8968ba38c47cf277b28dd5a51ff2f352b1ca","tid":946931,"uid":21842,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T01:41:54.000Z","msg":"上次歐聯對巴塞前又係度串美斯入唔到佢波， 點知最後被美斯入兩粒收左佢皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e791e47ab10f09c235fc71fcfefcaf4e89a87ba","tid":946931,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T01:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea89fdee7a7880f280774c5e5d262e97119436f6","tid":946931,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"745e8968ba38c47cf277b28dd5a51ff2f352b1ca","tid":946931,"uid":21842,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":1